      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system to achieve a breathtaking 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained with proactive rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The suspension remains tight with factory-spec bushings, preserving the iconic 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. An unmolested, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
