      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies the 'used' label. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-fresh appearance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather interior still carries that new-car scent, with every surface\u2014from the hand-stitched dashboard to the pristine carpets\u2014appearing untouched. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless; it has been serviced exclusively by authorized technicians using OEM parts, with a comprehensive logbook to prove its pampered history. Every feature, button, and sensor functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new machine. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
